/* -------------------------
 *
 * cursor sharing reason
 *
 * ------------------------- */
PRO <a name="share_r"></a><details open><br/><summary id="summary2">Cursor Sharing and Reason (GV$SQL_SHARED_CURSOR)</summary>
PRO
PRO Collected from GV$SQL_SHARED_CURSOR.
PRO
PRO <table>
PRO
PRO <tr>
PRO <th>#</th>
PRO <th>Reason</th>
